=== Proper Noun ===
'''Tigris'''
# A 1150-meter-long river in Southwest [[Asia]]. It flows South Southeast. It forms the Eastern edge of classical [[Mesopotamia]]. It unites with the [[Eufrates]] before flowing into the [[Persian Gulf]].
